                                    server creation-express
                        
                        1. create server folder
                        
                        2. install package.json  -  npm init

                        3. create index.json

                        4. install express  -  npm i express

                        5. import express in index.js

                        6. create app using express

                        7. set port
                        
                        8. run server  -  node index.js

                        9. define router  :  -expressApp.HTTPmethod(path,call back function)  

                        10. RUN SERVER - nodemon index.js

                        11. install & import session : npm i express-session

                        12.Middlewares - 

                            12.1 Application specific middleware

                            12.2 router specific middleware

                        13. JSON Web token - npm i jsonwebtoken ---used for authentication

                            13.1 token generation

                            13.2 token validation

                        14.MongoDB connection: 

                           14.1 install mangoose: sy: npm i mangoose

                        15. solving asynchronus events - promise

